    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont know. everything is just getting so hard lately. the doctors keep saying more things are failing and my kids... they're so busy with their own lives. i feel like im just a chore for them now. a constant thing they have to manage. i hate seeing that look in my son's eyes when he visits. like he's just checking a box.",
