    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "rest... i guess. but it's more than just being tired. i just feel like i'm taking up space that doesn't belong to me anymore. everyone is always so stressed because of my appointments and my health. if i wasn't around, i think they'd actually be able to breathe. it almost feels like i'm doing them a favor by just... stepping out of the way. do you think people ever feel like they're just a weight on everyone else?",
